=Query for Sources=

{{{field|Override source query|input type=checkbox|show on select=new-source-query}}} A standard query for sources will be inserted automatically. If you need to change this query, check the box.

<div id="new-source-query">You can override the standard query using this text area. This could be a different query, more than one query, or some text explaining why a query isn't appropriate.

{{{field|Source query|input type=textarea|rows=20}}}

For reference, the code for the standard query is shown below. You can copy this into the text area above and adapt it if you need to.

<pre>{{#ask:
[[Relates to::{{PAGENAME}}]]
|?Has description=Description
|default=No linked sources found.
}}</pre>
</div>

{{{end template}}}

